abstract: >
  Systematic extraction and assessment of research methodology, evidence,
  claims, and reproducibility infrastructure from academic papers in HASS
  disciplines. Implements a 7-pass workflow for evaluating transparency,
  replicability, and credibility of fieldwork-based research through
  evidence/claims extraction, RDMAP (Research Design and Methods Assessment
  Protocol), and FAIR infrastructure assessment.
